     | |+---------+          +-------+|              |\n             +-----+                          | ||  nodeB  +-lub-+    | nodeB ||              |\n     +-----+          +-----+                 | |+---------+     |    +-------+|              |\n     | bts |          | bts |                 | |         +------+-------+     |              |\n     +-----+          +-----+                 | |         |      |       |     |              |\n                                              | |      +--+-+  +-+-+  +--+-+   |              |\n                                              | |      |cell|  |...|  |cell|   |              |\n                                              | |RNS   +----+  +---+  +----+   |              |\n                                              | |                              |              |\n                                              | +------------------------------+              |\n                                              +----utran---------------------------utran------+\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                                                       +--------------+\n                                                       | sms-G/iw_msc |\n                                                       +--+-----------+\n  +--+        +-----+      +-------+    +-----------+     |    +-----+           +-----+\n  |ms|        | bts +------+  bsc  +----+  msc/vlr  +-----|----+ hlr +-----------+ auc |\n  +--+        +-----+      +---+-+-+    +---------+-+     |    +---+-+           +-----+\n                               | |                |  +-Gd-+        |\n                               | |               Gs  +---Gr--------+\n                               | |                |  |\n  +--+         +------------+  | +------Gb-------++--+--+          +------+             +-------------+\n  |ms|         |  edge_tru  +--+            +----+ sgsn |          | ggsn +----Gi-------+ isp_network |\n  +--+         +------------+               |    +-----++        