___\n\nAll the controlling signals are in the time slot 0 of the Multi-frame\nifk: \n\n     result from the fdma (and this one is a combined_channel)--+\n                                                                |\n     +----------------------------------------------------------+----+\n     |                                                               |\n\n     |               |              |               |                |\n     +---------------+--------------+---------------+----------------+....\n     |               |              |               |                |\n\n     |               |\n     +-+-------------+\n       +--- divided by 8 (0 ... 8)\n       |        and ctrl signals are in the time_slot_nb0\n       |  \n       +---     dedicated ctrl signals are in time slot_nb1 \n\n  \nin non-combined-channels:\n_______________________________\n\nDedicated controlling signals are in time slot 1 of the Multi-frame\n\n',NULL,NULL,'2015-02-27 13:27:04'),(862,'#gsm -architecture -with-interfaces','\n                              +---+\n                              |auc|\n                              +-+-+\n                                |\n                                h\n                                |\n                              +-+-+       +---+            +---+\n              +-----h---------+hlr+---d---+vlr|            |eir|\n         +----+           +-c-+---+       +-+-+            +-+-+\n         |gmsc|           |                 |                |\n         +----+           +-c-+---+         |                |\n              |               |msc+----b----+                |\n              +---------------+-+-+-----------------f--------+\n                                a\n                                |\n                              +-+-+\n                              |bsc|\n                              +---+\n\n                                .\n                                .\n                                .\n                